  - ID: 100028
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "3\uBC88 \uC774\uC0C1\uC73C\uB85C \uC644\uC218\uD560\uB54C\uB9C8\uB2E4
      \uB9C8\uBC95\uC774 \uC870\uAE08\uC529 \uAC15\uB825\uD574\uC9C0\uB294 \uCF64\uBCF4
      \uC0C1\uD0DC\uAC00 \uB418\uACE0."
    Text_EN: And, whenever you complete it three times or more, you enter a combo
      state... where the magic gets a little stronger each time.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100029
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130\uB97C \uCC98\uCE58\uD560 \uB54C\uB9C8\uB2E4 \uACBD\uD5D8\uCE58\uB97C
      \uC5BB\uC744 \uC218\uB3C4 \uC788\uC9C0!"
    Text_EN: Psst! Every single time you take down a monster, you actually get XP,
      you know?!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100030
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uACBD\uD5D8\uCE58\uB97C \uCC44\uC6E0\uC73C\uB2C8 \uC131\uC7A5\uC744
      \uD560 \uB54C\uB124!"
    Text_EN: And since you've completely filled up your XP bar, it is officially
