  - ID: 100348
    GroupID: 3011
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC624\uC154"
    name_EN: Ocea
    Text_KR: "\uC9C0\uAE08\uBD80\uD130 \uD558\uB294 \uC774\uC57C\uAE30\uB294 \uC5B4\uB514\uAE4C\uC9C0\uB098
      \uC5D0\uD544\uB85C\uADF8\uC77C\uC138. "
    Text_EN: Bear in mind that the story I share from this moment on... is nothing
      more than an epilogue.
