    GroupID: 3011
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC624\uC154"
    name_EN: Ocea
    Text_KR: "\uC6B0\uB9AC\uAC00 \uC9C4\uC8FC\uB97C \uCC3E\uC544\uC11C \uB3CC\uC544\uC654\uC744
      \uB54C, "
    Text_EN: When we finally found the pearl and made our return,
